A four year old survives an accident that kills her entire family&nbsp; A four year old little girl lost her Mother(33)sister(6)and grandparents in an accident &nbsp;on Sunday afternoon. The accident happened on the N1 between Mokopane &nbsp;and Mookgophong. The accident claimed seven lives when two sedans going in different directions collided head on head. Both cars had 5 passengers inside. The four year old and three other survivors were rushed to Mokopane hospital. Her injuries are severe buy she's stable. Internal injuries tests were done and results are still awaited.